I'm close to in my life.

27
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:49,460
So, I hate it when people hurt them.

28
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:51,140
I never want anyone to hurt my friends,

29
00:02:51,140 --> 00:02:52,540
